---
title: Halloumi Shakshuka with Lemon and Herb Couscous
description: We love good Halloumi Shakshuka with Couscous and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/halloumi-shakshuka-5816cd3a-65a5eb0f.jpg
